name: TechQuiz

”Alexa, start tech quiz”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tech quiz
des:
Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa. But this is no ordinary quiz. Brought to you by Quiz Club IIT KGP, this quiz is a bank for all the questions that will make your mind turn rather than the usual "Who's Who" & "What's that" that we consider as quizzing. 

While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
